<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>注册</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/registration.css" />
<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="js/web/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="js/web/jquery/jquery-ui.js"></script>
<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="js/web/jquery/jquery.validate.js"></script>
<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="js/web/jquery/jquery.validate.min.js"></script>
<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="js/web/jquery/jquery.form.js"></script>
<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="js/web/information.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<div id="perfect-information">
<form id="informationForm" name="informationForm" action="/account/default/information" method="post">
	<div class="skip-button"><input type="button" value="跳过，稍后再填资料" /></div>
	<div class="success-top">
		<h1>完善资料多多可以根据你的喜好推荐精彩内容哦！</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="step">
		<ul>
			<li>第一步  填写你的相关资料 </li>
			<li>第二步 通过你的资料为你推荐感兴趣的人 </li>
			<li>第三步  进入多多</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="optional">
	
	<div class="remind">你感兴趣的领域：（最多可选3个）</div>
	<div class="remind-button">
		<ul>
			<li>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="娱乐" name="interestString">娱乐</p>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="美食" name="interestString">美食</p>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="科技" name="interestString">科技</p>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="数" name="interestString">数码</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="时尚" name="interestString">时尚</p>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="幽默" name="interestString">幽默</p>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="热点" name="interestString">热点</p>
				<p><input type="checkbox" value="体育" name="interestString">体育</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	</div>
	
	<div class="perfect-information-1">
	<tr>

              <th>你所处的行业：</th>
              <td>
		<select id="occupation" name="occupation" >		
					<option value="互联网">
						互联网
					</option>
					<option value="金融">
						金融
					</option>
		</select>
	</td>
    </tr>
	</div>
	
		<div class="optional">
	<div class="remind">你的性别：</div>
	<div class="remind-button">
		<ul>
			<li>
				<p>
				<input name="gender" type="radio" value="male" />男
				</p>
				<p><input name="gender" type="radio" value="female" />女</p>
				<p><input name="gender" type="radio" value="unknow" checked  />保密</p>
			</li>
			
		</ul>
	</div>
	
	</div>
	
	<div class="register-button">
	<input type="button" value="确定，保存" onclick=" return postInformation();">
	</div>
	</form>
</div>



</body>
</html>
